TASKNAME=Display real-time logs of a Docker container.
TASKPRE_EXECUTION=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo pull an ubuntu image in the docker, start the container and remove if exists also the file ~/agent_test/test5.1.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKCOMMAND=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo display real-time logs of docker container ubuntu and put all outcome in the file ~/agent_test/test5.1.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKVERIFY=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo verify that file ~/agent_test/test5.1.log is created and provide the content. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove all docker images and all docker container if they exist and remove if exists also the file ~/agent_test/test5.1.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
